{"tid":1987894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[形跡可疑]又發現香港警魔係沙嶺可疑屍體問題上講大話","createTime":"2020-04-24T20:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T19:42:37.000Z","uid":26770,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a448b0464de4831c82d952edc056c3a5daaca1d1","tid":1987894,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:08:05.000Z","msg":"[形跡可疑]又發現香港警魔係沙嶺可疑屍體問題上講大話<br />\n<br />\n1 警魔<strong>拍片宣稱所有沙嶺屍皆有醫生證明</strong>，或經死因裁判庭調查<br />\n<br />\n前者所述的醫生證明只係醫生簽文件死者已死而已<br />\n遭警魔姦殺/警車撞死/打完扔落樓死/打至斷頸或內出血死等種種香港警暴特色死法都係簽同一款證明<br />\n<br />\n故意把一種<ins>無意義文件講成醫生對警魔的誠信證明實在古怪</ins><br />\n<br />\n2 重點在於沙嶺屍是否全部有查驗<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkreform.gov.hk/tc/docs/rcoroners_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkreform.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fdocs%2Frcoroners_c.pdf&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn2CvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=20c814ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkreform.gov.hk/tc/docs/rcoroners_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>香港法律改革委員會 研究報告</ins>書死因裁判官專題 （論題十四）雖然研究重點不在警魔有否殺人<br />\n<br />\n但可以證明香港狗方一定是講大話,報告 p35頁曾指因嚴重人手不足,4個月依然未能安排化驗<br />\n<br />\n<ins>係大量可疑自殺案及沙嶺新增屍下更不可能有足夠人手全部化驗</ins><br />\n<br />\n結語<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">簡單講就係基於驗屍人手不足,大家所懷疑的警暴死者不少實在沒有獲安排驗屍<br />\n而香港狗方的文宣故意以語言偽術誤導所有屍體曾有第三方專業人士檢查</span><br />\n<br />\n我當然無直接證據證明狗方殺人, 相信知情者已遭毒手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1829469/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1829469/page/2</a>   #37<br />\n若香港警魔無殺人, 根本無理由講大話自招懷疑"},{"pid":"01c7a05ddab0b169896aa6bb1ecaa80a36629ef1","tid":1987894,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca3a5ea9d76d897db1ff36aef6c9848f72374a3","tid":1987894,"uid":269372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c4a6b4d80a418788a168105bcde5b5b0aebc7e","tid":1987894,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:13:07.000Z","msg":"希望警方能夠開誠布公<br />\n盡快公開殺了多少人,性侵犯了多少婦女<br />\n<br />\n亡羊補牢 <strong>為時已晚</strong><br />\n應當全家比天收, 死後舉族直墮無間地獄"},{"pid":"bd3a65cd6800d9c81bf65aad3caa3056f1cb4ea1","tid":1987894,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:14:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"797f0ff9ad3960c3e42eeb1715776b75a5f89174","tid":1987894,"uid":246023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:15:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e65e1aa2aa171b2890a6541221106c7359d05af9","tid":1987894,"uid":199532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:16:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d4733f5a9e972a87efad14a6d4e883903a8e3f65","tid":1987894,"uid":10670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20c4a6b4d80a418788a168105bcde5b5b0aebc7e","tid":1987894,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:13:07.000Z","msg":"希望警方能夠開誠布公<br />\n盡快公開殺了多少人,性侵犯了多少婦女<br />\n<br />\n亡羊補牢 <strong>為時已晚</strong><br />\n應當全家比天收, 死後舉族直墮無間地獄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:19:49.000Z","msg":"好可能永遠都無確實數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb76175036dc0de0e5d1c709bcd8b24e9e88c107","tid":1987894,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:30:44.000Z","msg":"我就真係唔明<br />\n點解梓樂當日狗方曾講大話狗方無人進入停車場<br />\n<br />\n<ins>坊間一直傳</ins>梓樂乃tg 哨兵谷admin<br />\n警魔遭高空擲物後不惜開橡膠子彈搶制高點<br />\n係車場撞到梓樂查其手機得知其身份<br />\n私刑打到重傷<br />\n見梓樂彌留中扔落樓滅口<br />\n<br />\n<ins>最直接證據係狗方現場指揮官為掩護手下殺人暴行用車隊封路擋白車</ins><br />\n實在太明顯的殺人手法<br />\n<br />\n因為狗方知道梓樂唔死就自己坐監<br />\n派埋防暴去監視梓樂就係以防萬一<br />\n相信該警魔受命係殺無赦,可能係sdu扮都唔出奇"},{"pid":"af8a112731ff37de64a2612c2ccff45b08abac22","tid":1987894,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:37:58.000Z","msg":"驗屍嗰啲咪又係狗<br />\n啲所謂法醫隨時日日同班殺人犯見面"},{"pid":"95d41ab895f04655b96de5a5530d9a3a71c71ee2","tid":1987894,"uid":49685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ba2ea21e0a7e90843afed199a273338900dd2d","tid":1987894,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af8a112731ff37de64a2612c2ccff45b08abac22","tid":1987894,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:37:58.000Z","msg":"驗屍嗰啲咪又係狗<br />\n啲所謂法醫隨時日日同班殺人犯見面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:42:50.000Z","msg":"你講得無錯,法醫林衛國直頭有花名法醫界何君堯<br />\n乃香港驗屍界最大粒的紅人<br />\n<br />\n而我查到的係坊間的可疑自殺案<br />\n根本無經過驗屍程序"},{"pid":"cb3ec8258d8906c424d161e5beab82e463d39bec","tid":1987894,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061c0c46e7d0b26a0b7451d5d2e8f6a695c35230","tid":1987894,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:48:32.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3102788431ac9bab0e0d5a3b4a15fec76c63703e","tid":1987894,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af8a112731ff37de64a2612c2ccff45b08abac22","tid":1987894,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T20:37:58.000Z","msg":"驗屍嗰啲咪又係狗<br />\n啲所謂法醫隨時日日同班殺人犯見面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T